xxl.functions
Class ArrayFactory

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--xxl.functions.Function
        |
        +--xxl.functions.ArrayFactory
public class ArrayFactory
extends Function

A Factory-method for Object-typed-arrays. The ArrayFactory creates an array and fills the array with Objects. An Iterator of arguments can be passed to the invoke-method of this class to create the objects which are stored in the array.
